title.rendered: Can I Transfer Dumpster to a New Device?

content.rendered:
Unfortunately, you can’t. 

However, you can try restoring the files to your old device and transfer them with the rest of your content to your new device. Then download Dumpster on your new device, and then delete the desired content.
